messages.message: yea david/I both wanted all tests to run on master (post-merge) but only delta’s to run pre-merge (on PRs), so folks were blocked as little as possible when wanting to merge a PR but if the “test the deltas” logic had problems, that popped up in the full master test.
All the builds are failing now since they're all timing out.
yea in that case we need to do do that or split the master job to happen on two workers
